#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:514
msgid "Lily Pad"
msgstr "荷葉"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_flowers/register.lua:515
msgid ""
"A lily pad is a flat plant block which can be walked on. They can be placed "
"on water sources, ice and frosted ice."
msgstr ""
"荷葉是一種平坦的植物方塊，可以在上面行走。它們可以放在水源、冰面和結霜的冰面"
"上。"
